title: It’s Mohanlal vs Manju Warrier this Navrathri
text:
The leads of Aaraam Thampuran - Mohanlal and Manju Warrier - will be competing this Navrathri with their respective releases, Kanal and Rani Padmini.
Mohanlal's movie, which is directed by M Padmakumar, is slated to hit the screens on Oct 22 while Rani Padmini , directed by Aashiq Abu, will release a day later.
Kanal stars Honey Rose and Anoop Menon along with Mohanlal. Rani Padmini is touted to be a travel movie with Rima Kallingal playing the other lead actress.
